A '''quest hall''' in a [[player-owned house]] is a room where the player can display quest achievements and awards. This room can be created with level 35 [[Construction]] and {{Coins|25000}}.

There are 8 [[hotspot]]s available:
*[[Bookcase space]]
*[[Guild trophy space]]
*[[Landscape space]]
*[[Map space]]
*[[Portrait space]]
*[[Rug space]]
*[[Stair space]]
*[[Sword space]]

